      <text x="265" y="118" fill="#a1a1aa" text-anchor="middle" font-size="12.5">コアウィーブ総確約(第1~3段階)</text>
      <rect x="352" y="52" width="158" height="94" rx="10" fill="#18181b" stroke="#3f3f46" stroke-width="1.3"/>
